node.text:
Which creative shot is your favorite? 🤔 You can check how to get your photos promoted in our account, use the link in our bio @tripfever

Hugo Suíssas is a Lisbon based creative photographer who proves that you can make any photo much more interesting by trying out a different perspective. He turns simple bridges and landscapes into surreal and fantastical places, and items like keys, fruits, and kids' toys into magical props.

Every single photograph has a different story and a different idea. They help us see the dull and boring world that we're used to in a new and more fun way.

Which one is your favorite? 1-2-3-4 or 5?
📷 @suissas

In Love with United Kingdom 🥰🇬🇧 We can promote your photos in our account. Check the link in our bio for instructions: @tripfever

Places and photos by:
1. Windsor Castle @piteshmistry
2. Cadgwith Cove @whatstacydid
3. Corston, Wiltshire @steve_parke
4. Edensor @fayazey
5. North Yorkshire @hope_and_wander
6. Isle of Wight @shadedcream
7. Burford @lensereflection
8. Blaise Hamlet @adamjason1
9. Bibury @the_onlycookiemonster
10. Stow on the Wold, Cotswolds @whatstacydid

The United Kingdom, made up of England, Scotland, Wales and Northern Ireland, is an island nation in northwestern Europe.

England – birthplace of Shakespeare and The Beatles –

is home to the capital, London, a globally influential centre of finance and culture.

England is also site of Neolithic Stonehenge, Bath’s Roman spa and centuries-old universities at Oxford and Cambridge. ❤🇬🇧

Swimming wild and free 🐢 You can check how to get your photos promoted in our account, use the link in our bio @tripfever

“So many nests breaking out every day!”

Each year thousands of baby turtles break out of their nests and swarm the beaches of Australia. Turtle nesting season is from November to March and the baby turtles hatch from January to May peaking around February.
⁠
📽 @aleksmutated
📍Heron Island, Queensland, Australia

Would you drive this? 😅 Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on tripfever.net (link in my bio: @tripfever)

This footage was taken in Borneo, the third-largest island in the world and the largest in Asia. Immerse in the Southeast Asia’s Malay Archipelago, is shared by the Malaysian states of Sabah and Sarawak, Indonesian Kalimantan and the tiny nation of Brunei. It’s known for its beaches and ancient, biodiverse rainforest, home to wildlife including orangutans and clouded leopards. In Sabah is 4,095m-tall Mount Kinabalu, the island’s highest peak, and, offshore, the famed dive site Sipadan Island.

📽 @khaiiidiir
📍 Kalimantan, Indonesia
🎶 JayCal PR - Me Llamaste
